{
  "60576": {
    "不知从何处传来了声音……": ""
  },
  "60577": {
    "<center>撼动人心，合二为一。\n将恩惠赐予这颗独一无二的心……": ""
  },
  "27942": {
    "<center>没有饱含心意的歌，就不能称为歌。\n心心相传，传达心意的话语能开拓道路。": ""
  },
  "27943": {
    "<center>恩惠之歌与引导之歌，两首歌传达心意。\n在撼动人心之处唱出这两首歌吧。": ""
  },
  "27944": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>我也派调查员去调查，\n撼动人心之处究竟所指哪里了，\n但还是找不到任何线索……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27945": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>撼动人心之处到底是什么？！\n为什么拉迪斯王不惜做到这种地步\n也要封印住男王之歌？！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27946": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>……抱歉，我大吼大叫的。\n一直没有头绪，\n我急躁了起来。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27947": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>现在我完全是一筹莫展。\n虽然很想借助你的力量，\n但就连要请你帮忙都不知道该从何着手……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27948": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>……哎呀，糟糕！\n就快到唱恩惠之歌的时间了。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27949": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00418 _normal m00001>好的，我们前往露台吧。<stop_lip_animation n00418 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27950": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>恩惠之歌……啊。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27951": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001><pc>，你既然都来了，\n就一起听听母亲大人的歌声吧。\n我们也立刻出发。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27952": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>…………<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27953": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>如果引导之歌没办法产生恩惠的效果，\n我就无法当国王……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27954": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>或许拉迪斯王也是在说……\n我没资格成为国王吧。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27955": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>……奥迪斯王子，\n你为什么想成为国王呢？<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27956": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>怎么了？塞莉娅，\n突然问这种问题。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27957": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>请你回答我。<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27958": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>……因为我想守护。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27959": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>守护母亲和父亲……不对，我是想成为国王，\n守护所有维纳群岛的人民。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27960": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>我的父亲以前也曾这么说。<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27961": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>……撼动人心之处，是智慧沉睡的遗迹。\n就在波纹音叉所指引的地方……<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27962": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>塞莉娅……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27963": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>撼动人心，合二为一。\n将恩惠赐予这颗独一无二的心……<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27964": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00419 _normal m00001>将这些话传达给波纹音叉……<stop_lip_animation n00419 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27965": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>……谢谢你，塞莉娅。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27966": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>母亲，我知道撼动人心之处是哪里了，\n是塞莉娅告诉我的。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27967": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00418 _normal m00001>……嗯，\n详情你就在女王大厅告诉我吧。<stop_lip_animation n00418 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27968": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001><pc>，你也一起来，\n我需要你的帮忙！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27969": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001><pc>，谢谢你。\n多亏有你帮忙，我才能把母亲\n平安带到这里。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27970": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>其实我是第一次来这里。\n原来恩惠之歌的效果就是靠着这支音叉\n扩散到整个群岛啊。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27971": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>我记得这支波纹音叉\n据说也是拉迪斯王制作的。\n他真是位伟大的国王啊……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27972": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>国王的石板上写着\n“传达心意的话语能开启大门”。\n我就来唱出塞莉娅说的那段话吧。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27973": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>撼动人心，合二为一。\n将恩惠赐予这颗独一无二的心……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27974": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>这……难不成就是旅途之门？\n这是要进去看看吧……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27975": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00418 _normal m00001>那我们就进去看看吧，\n去看看前方究竟有什么。<stop_lip_animation n00418 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27976": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>我和母亲先进去，\n<pc>你也快来吧。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27977": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>哦，<pc>，女王平安无事吗？\n没遇到怪物袭击吧？\n没有因为旅途劳累弄坏了身体吧？<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27978": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>你听好了！虽说王子就在旁边，\n你也一定要照顾好女王！<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27981": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>这里毫无疑问就是撼动人心之处了。\n但是，又只有石板啊……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27982": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>上面刻着很多小字。\n总之读一遍吧。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27983": {
    "<center>光靠我们的力量是无法毁灭暴君的。\n剩下的方法只有一个。": ""
  },
  "27984": {
    "<center>那就是将暴君封印在时间静止的永恒之水里，\n然后由人看守。\n这本来是我这个国王的责任。": ""
  },
  "27985": {
    "<center>但是，也就等于要抛下那些\n奋力从绝望中站起来的维迪百姓。\n我直到最后都一直在苦恼。": ""
  },
  "27986": {
    "<center>就在我还迟迟无法下定决心的某天，\n我的女儿塞莉娅带着暴君\n一同进入了永恒之水。": ""
  },
  "27987": {
    "<center>……大概是看穿了我的犹豫不决吧，\n塞莉娅她就这样代替我\n自己成为封印的巫女。": ""
  },
  "27988": {
    "<center>我牺牲了我最爱的家人。\n家人是我的无价之宝，\n是我就算赌上性命也要守护的宝物。": ""
  },
  "27989": {
    "<center>我悲叹不已……\n我诅咒起身为国王\n却不敢牺牲的自己。": ""
  },
  "27990": {
    "<center>然后……我就顿悟了。": ""
  },
  "27991": {
    "<center>身为父亲，必须保护亲爱的家人，\n这才是我作为男人的职责。": ""
  },
  "27992": {
    "<center>于是我将王位让给妻子，\n放弃了国王的身份。": ""
  },
  "27993": {
    "<center>之后我就禁止了男人继承王位。\n王族的男人就应该将全部力量\n用来保护自己的家人。": ""
  },
  "27994": {
    "<center>拿到这块石板的人啊，\n你想要打破禁令\n成为国王吧？": ""
  },
  "27995": {
    "<center>如果你既能当王，\n也能保护好家人的话，\n就将你的坚定信念在此展现出来吧。": ""
  },
  "27996": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>这样啊……原来拉迪斯王\n禁止男王，\n是因为塞莉娅成了封印的巫女啊……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27997": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>不过，要怎么展现出\n坚定的信念……？<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27998": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>怎么了？！怎么回事？<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "27999": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>轰隆……我是拉迪斯誓言的见证人，\n名叫拉迪斯奥。<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28000": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>如果你能超越拉迪斯誓言的力量，\n就来打倒我吧……<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28001": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>母亲，请退下！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28002": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>看样子是要我打败这家伙\n来展现自己坚定的信念。\n嘿<cs_pchero>，你也助我一臂之力吧！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28003": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>轰隆————……！！<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28006": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001><cs_pchero>！这家伙\n相当难对付！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28007": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>我必须保护母亲！\n你助我一臂之力吧！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28008": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>如果你能超越拉迪斯誓言的力量，\n就来打倒我吧……<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28009": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>轰隆————……！！<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28010": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>……<cs_pchero>，干得漂亮。\n结果我从头到尾都在依赖你啊。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28011": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>什么？！这家伙还没死！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28012": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>轰隆——……！<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28013": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>母亲————————！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28014": {
    "<start_lip_sync m12304 _normal m00001>轰隆——你竟然把我打倒……了。<stop_lip_animation m12304 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28015": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>父……父亲？！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28016": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>拉迪斯流的剑术……\n让我用上了，拉迪斯王。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28017": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>奥迪斯，你听着！<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28018": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>正如国王的石板上所写，\n我们王族的男人无论如何\n就是要把守护家人放在第一位。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28019": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>尚未成家的你\n或许对此没有深切感受，\n但这份责任可是极其重大……<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28020": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>一个国王必须守护国家，\n同时也要保护重要的家人，\n而你要肩负起这两种责任。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28021": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>我不认为现在的你有能力做到这些。\n不过，只要今后你抱着连死都无所畏惧的决心\n持续努力，或许就能做到。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28022": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>你有这样的决心吗？<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28023": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>有……我有……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28024": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>……有决心的人是这样回答的吗？<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28025": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>有！我有决心，\n家人和人民都要保护，我要成为国王，\n保护所有生活在维纳群岛上的人！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28026": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>无论这条道路多么艰难坎坷，\n我绝不会退缩！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28027": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00421 _normal m00001>那么，你就与女王一同歌唱吧。<stop_lip_animation n00421 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28028": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00418 _normal m00001>来吧，奥迪斯，歌唱吧。\n如今的你一定能懂得引导之歌的精髓。<stop_lip_animation n00418 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28029": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>……我知道了，母亲！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28030": {
    "<center>……海中生，海中栖。\n此乃吾等，维迪之民。": ""
  },
  "28031": {
    "<center>我们向大海母亲祈祷，\n请将恩泽赐予众生。": ""
  },
  "28032": {
    "<center>伟大的海神啊，\n请守护我们的生命，\n净化我们的思想……": ""
  },
  "28033": {
    "<center>凶猛的大海啊，平息下来。\n怒吼的大海啊，平息下来。": ""
  },
  "28034": {
    "<center>大海父亲教导我们。\n激流孕育着生命。": ""
  },
  "28035": {
    "<center>伟大的海神啊，\n实现我们的愿望，\n守护我们的誓言……": ""
  },
  "28036": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>成功了……成功了！\n养育的效果终于出现了！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28037": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00418 _normal m00001>这样奥迪斯就得到成为国王的资格了。\n应该不会再有人阻止\n男性当王了吧。<stop_lip_animation n00418 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28038": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>谢谢你，<cs_pchero>！\n多亏有你的帮忙，\n这下我也能成为国王了！！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28039": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>我们回威里纳德城吧，\n我还要给<cs_pchero>你谢礼呢！<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28040": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>那么，阿贝卢克团长本来就知道\n父亲他剑术一流？<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28041": {
    "<start_lip_sync n01486 _normal m00001>是的！由于梅尔公爵有令\n不准泄漏此事，\n我也无法告诉王子。<stop_lip_animation n01486 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28042": {
    "<start_lip_sync n01486 _normal m00001>梅尔公爵以前可是被誉为威里纳德剑神的\n传奇魔法战士。<stop_lip_animation n01486 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28043": {
    "<start_lip_sync n01486 _normal m00001>就算我们王立魔法战士团的魔法战士\n所有人一起上也敌不过他。<stop_lip_animation n01486 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28044": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>有……有那么厉害啊……\n可是，父亲有那样的传说，\n有如此的实力，我竟然都不知道……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28045": {
    "<start_lip_sync n01486 _normal m00001>梅尔公爵进入王室以后，\n就立誓自己这份力量只会用于\n保护女王蒂奥蕾大人。<stop_lip_animation n01486 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28046": {
    "<start_lip_sync n01486 _normal m00001>那个传说在当时就被掩埋起来了。\n梅尔公爵是隐藏在威里纳德王国中\n最强的守护者，也是真正的魔法战士。<stop_lip_animation n01486 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28047": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>真没想到父亲如此厉害，\n我以前实在是瞎了眼……<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28048": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>哦！<pc>，你来了啊。\n抱歉让你久等了。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28049": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001>这次真的谢谢你的帮忙。\n来，这边请，酬劳已经准备好了。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "28050": {
    "<start_lip_sync n00417 _normal m00001><pc>，我要再次对你表示感谢。\n多亏有你，我才能得到成为国王的资格。\n收下这份酬劳吧。<stop_lip_animation n00417 CLOSE_MOUTH>": ""
  },
  "42173": {
